---
title: Mexican Popcorn Chicken & Garlic Rice with Charred Corn-Tomato Salsa & Smokey Aioli
description: Tonight’s chicken is really ‘popping off’ (please forgive the pun). A touch of heat and fun Mexican-inspired flavours come together to create chicken that will be popping with flavour (sorry we couldn’t help it). Add some fragrant garlic rice and a smokey sweetcorn and tomato salsa, and it’s bound to be a pop-ular dish (okay we’re done now).

